
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Low Balance Alert</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #ff9800; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }
        .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background: #ff9800; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Low Balance Alert</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{tenantName}},</p>
            <p>Your balance for <strong>{{addOnName}}</strong> is running low.</p>
            <p><strong>Remaining Credits:</strong> {{remainingCredits}}</p>
            <p><strong>Alert Threshold:</strong> {{threshold}}</p>
            {{#if autoRenew}}
            <p>Auto-renewal is enabled, so we'll automatically purchase more credits when needed.</p>
            {{else}}
            <p>Please purchase additional credits to avoid service interruption.</p>
            {{/if}}
            {{#if purchaseUrl}}
            <p><a href="{{purchaseUrl}}" class="button">Purchase Credits</a></p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>LaundryPro Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>